    <div class="simple-concept-box">
        <h4><i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i> Key Idea</h4>
        <p>Cryptography changes normal messages (called "plaintext") into scrambled code (called "ciphertext"). Only people with the right key can unscramble it back to read the message.</p>
